The paper deals with the detection of suspicious emails using machine learning algorithms and feature selection techniques. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as it involves identifying and preventing potential threats. The use of machine learning algorithms and feature selection also suggests that the paper could be categorized under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) as it deals with the analysis of email content. Finally, the paper could also be categorized under software engineering (cs.SE) as it proposes a model for detecting suspicious emails.
